QuestData.Title: Bleeding Hollow Supplies
QuestData.Description: The orcish ruins of Zeth'Gor to the southeast serve as a base for an ever-growing tide of orcs emerging from Hellfire Citadel.$B$BThe Sons of Lothar have been fighting them for some time, and the stories they tell would be nigh unbelievable if I hadn't seen these 'fel' orcs with my own eyes.$B$BSomething has changed them, augmented them in a way we've never seen before. We have to do anything we can to keep them from strengthening. Go to Zeth'Gor and destroy any supplies you find there.
QuestData.LogDescription: Destroy 6 piles of Bleeding Hollow Supplies and report to Lieutenant Amadi at Honor Hold.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Return to Lieutenant Amadi at Honor Hold in Hellfire Peninsula.
